com.github.andreptb.fitnesse.selenium

Class ByWebElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openqa.selenium.By
      • com.github.andreptb.fitnesse.selenium.ByWebElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ByWebElement
extends org.openqa.selenium.By
implements Serializable
    A special selector with returns a previously retrieved element. It does perform any actual searching. The found element might no longer valid on the remote, resulting in failures when any actions are performed.
    See Also:
